6
00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:50.710
Gyukimaru of Bandit's Bridge

7
00:01:52.420 --> 00:01:53.590
Ka...

8
00:01:53.590 --> 00:01:54.970
Kawa...

9
00:01:54.970 --> 00:01:56.760
Kawamatsu?!

10
00:01:57.130 --> 00:01:59.260
Is it...

11
00:01:59.260 --> 00:02:00.760
really you?!

12
00:02:04.350 --> 00:02:06.230
You're alive!

13
00:02:07.480 --> 00:02:12.520
I am... despite having eaten nothing but
rotten fish for the past thirteen years.

14
00:02:14.900 --> 00:02:17.740
Let me see your face, Kawamatsu!

15
00:02:17.740 --> 00:02:20.620
Alas, I am in shackles.

16
00:02:20.620 --> 00:02:21.870
What?!

17
00:02:24.790 --> 00:02:26.950
When will the battle start?

18
00:02:26.950 --> 00:02:29.920
Nine days from now,
on the night of the Fire Festival!

19
00:02:29.920 --> 00:02:35.340
Chopping off Kaido's head during his own
festival is a great way to pay tribute to him!

20
00:02:35.340 --> 00:02:39.380
Forgive me, Raizo, but could you
help me get out of here first?!

21
00:02:39.380 --> 00:02:42.760
Of course I will! I'll get right to it!

22
00:02:42.760 --> 00:02:48.180
It seems I will need the keys to both the cage
and the cuffs before I can free you.

23
00:02:48.180 --> 00:02:51.100
Indeed. Although the rust
may inhibit their opening.

24
00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:54.230
There's someone at the forbidden cell!

25
00:02:54.230 --> 00:02:55.270
Who's that?!

26
00:02:55.270 --> 00:02:56.940
That's the guy!

27
00:02:56.940 --> 00:02:58.240
Master Solitaire!

28
00:02:58.240 --> 00:03:01.280
We found the key thief
from the Executive Tower!

29
00:03:02.620 --> 00:03:04.410
Don't let him escape!

30
00:03:05.620 --> 00:03:07.290
Oh no!

31
00:03:07.290 --> 00:03:09.160
Smoke Escape Technique!

32
00:03:11.290 --> 00:03:12.590
He vanished!

33
00:03:12.590 --> 00:03:13.880
He must be a ninja!

34
00:03:13.880 --> 00:03:15.380
Find him!

35
00:03:18.510 --> 00:03:23.760
All right, leave the key thief
to the others and...

36
00:03:24.300 --> 00:03:27.140
bring the thing here!

37
00:03:36.020 --> 00:03:37.570
Alright...

38
00:03:37.570 --> 00:03:40.280
We've got some fools to execute!

39
00:03:40.280 --> 00:03:41.740
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

40
00:03:41.740 --> 00:03:43.820
Hey! Come this way!

41
00:03:44.660 --> 00:03:47.910
Here we go!

42
00:04:04.840 --> 00:04:08.010
Give it up for Superstar Queen's
Special Device Performance:

43
00:04:08.010 --> 00:04:11.980
The Sumo Inferno!

44
00:04:13.480 --> 00:04:15.020
Sumo?

45
00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:17.440
What the...?!

46
00:04:20.570 --> 00:04:24.570
This is the same collar
we just put on you guys!

47
00:04:25.070 --> 00:04:27.950
Imagine this stone pillar is you!

48
00:04:27.950 --> 00:04:32.120
Leave the ring with that thing on and...

49
00:04:38.420 --> 00:04:40.460
How scary!

50
00:04:40.460 --> 00:04:47.970
As you just saw, the moment you go
out of bounds, sharp blades are ejected,

51
00:04:47.970 --> 00:04:51.430
instantly lopping off your head!

52
00:04:51.430 --> 00:04:55.060
Damn! It's just like
the Celestial Dragons' collars!

53
00:04:55.060 --> 00:04:59.730
And of course it's designed so that you can't
forcibly remove it, so don't even try!

54
00:04:59.730 --> 00:05:04.570
You'll be fine as long as you
keep winning sumo matches!

55
00:05:04.570 --> 00:05:06.990
But leaving the ring is instant death!

56
00:05:06.990 --> 00:05:12.290
You're a tag team! Consider the execution
a success once you're both outside the ring!

57
00:05:12.290 --> 00:05:16.960
But if you change your mind
and join our crew,

58
00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:19.960
I'll spare you alone, Straw Hat!

59
00:05:19.960 --> 00:05:24.880
Our side will use weapons,
fight in numbers, and won't be wearing collars!

60
00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:27.680
We'll deploy as many people as we want.

61
00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:31.120
That's why I'll do you this one favor:

62
00:05:31.120 --> 00:05:33.980
I'll remove your seastone cuffs!

63
00:05:37.650 --> 00:05:40.110
Wh-Whaaat?!

64
00:05:40.110 --> 00:05:42.780
After all the trouble I went to!

65
00:05:43.690 --> 00:05:47.450
Wait, does that mean this is not
the key to Sir Luffy's cuffs?!

66
00:05:49.370 --> 00:05:51.120
Yay!

67
00:05:51.120 --> 00:05:54.250
You're a nice guy after all!

68
00:05:54.250 --> 00:05:57.040
This means you're letting us out!

69
00:05:57.040 --> 00:06:00.330
Aren't you forgetting about the collar?

70
00:06:00.330 --> 00:06:02.960
Now there's something worse on you!

71
00:06:04.550 --> 00:06:05.880
Oh, yeah.

72
00:06:05.880 --> 00:06:07.630
Wait a minute!

73
00:06:07.630 --> 00:06:11.800
I will just hold Straw Hat back
if we're on the same team!

74
00:06:11.800 --> 00:06:14.310
Could you at least execute us separately?!

75
00:06:14.310 --> 00:06:15.980
Hey, balloon!

76
00:06:17.060 --> 00:06:17.850
Balloon?!

77
00:06:19.690 --> 00:06:21.310
Straw Hat!

78
00:06:21.310 --> 00:06:24.190
If I kick your ass...

79
00:06:24.190 --> 00:06:26.490
will you let us out of here?!

